description: The fund adviser employs a “passive management” investment approach designed to track the total return performance, before fees and expenses, of the index. The index is a rules-based index that consists of U.S.- and Canada-listed companies engaged in the Residential and Apartment Real Estate Business. Under normal circumstances, the fund invests at least 80% of its net assets in Residential and Apartment Real Estate Companies. The fund is non-diversified.
name: Kelly Residential & Apartment Real Estate ETF
